    <content type="html">&lt;div class="govspeak"&gt;&lt;p&gt;This consultation covers amendments to the new firefighters’ pension scheme (England), as set out in the Firefighters’ Pension Scheme (England) Order 2006.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This is so that fire and rescue authorities can comply with their duties for automatic enrolment under workplace pension reform.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</content>
